OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wed 29 Apr to Fri 8 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to lie close
OL,7,Fto the UK at the start of this period.
OL,8,FMost places will be dry with sunny
OL,9,Fspells and light winds, although there
OL,10,Fcould be some overnight mist and fog.
OL,11,FInto the first week of May, conditions
OL,12,Fwill probably become more changeable
OL,13,Fwith low pressure systems becoming
OL,14,Fmore likely. This means an increasing
OL,15,Fchance of showers or longer spells of
OL,16,Frain, with a risk of strong winds at
OL,17,Ftimes. Temperatures are likely to be
OL,18,Fclose to or slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
