OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 9 May to Sat 23 MayFLow
OL,6,Fpressure systems will probably
OL,7,Fdominate across the UK at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period. This means showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain are likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, heavy in places with a risk of
OL,11,Fstrong winds. Temperatures will
OL,12,Fprobably be close to or slightly below
OL,13,Fnormal. Later in the month more
OL,14,Fsettled, drier conditions may begin to
OL,15,Fdevelop with temperatures perhaps
OL,16,Frising slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
